max_tokens / unknown / length / content_filter / refusal cannot pay; fallback with stop follows
normal gates; fallback with absent/abnormal cannot pay). Existing completion mocks updated to
send an explicit stop where they exercise the valid-content path.

If the real gateway omits this metadata, the fix is in the adapter — the money gate is not
loosened to accommodate missing data. Not deployed.

